  "general_information": "The Golar Nanook is a FSRU/LNG carrier vessel built by Samsung Heavy Industries, completed in October 2018. It has a length of 306m and a beam of 43.4m, with four GTT Mark III storage tanks for a total capacity of 170,000m^3. The vessel features a sea water direct type re-gasification system and is equipped with a yoke mooring system forward, quick release hook, and four fenders for safe ship to ship LNG transfer.",
